comment0.target=Triangulo
comment0.text=\r\n\ Un\ tri\u221A\u00B0ngulo\ que\ se\ puede\ modificar\ y\ que\ se\ dibuja\ a\ s\u221A\u2260\ mismo\ en\ un\ canvas.\r\n\ \r\n\ @author\ \ Michael\ K\u221A\u2202lling\ and\ David\ J.\ Barnes\r\n\ @version\ 2016.02.29\r\n\r\n\ @translation\ Maximiliano\ Andr\u221A\u00A9s\ Eschoyez\ y\ Mart\u221A\u2260n\ Federico\ Pelliza\ (2025)\r\n
comment1.params=
comment1.target=Triangulo()
comment1.text=\r\n\ Crea\ un\ nuevo\ tri\u221A\u00B0ngulo\ en\ una\ posici\u221A\u2265n\ y\ color\ por\ defecto.\r\n
comment10.params=distancia
comment10.target=void\ moverLentoHorizontal(java.lang.Integer)
comment10.text=\r\n\ Mueve\ lentamente\ el\ tri\u221A\u00B0ngulo\ horizontalmente\ 'distancia'\ p\u221A\u2260xeles.\r\n
