comment12.target=void\ changeSize(java.lang.Integer,\ java.lang.Integer)
comment12.text=\r\n\ Cambia\ el\ tama\u221A\u00B1o\ (en\ p\u221A\u2260xeles).\ Debe\ ser\ >\=\ 0.\r\n
comment13.params=newColor
comment13.target=void\ changeColor(java.lang.String)
comment13.text=\r\n\ Cambia\ el\ color.\ Los\ colores\ v\u221A\u00B0lidos\ son\ "red",\ "yellow",\ "blue",\r\n\ "green",\ "magenta"\ y\ "black".\r\n
