comment14.target=void\ draw()
comment14.text=\r\n\ Dibuja\ el\ tri\u221A\u00B0ngulo\ en\ la\ pantalla\ seg\u221A\u222Bn\ especifica\ su\ estado.\r\n
comment15.params=
comment15.target=void\ erase()
